  h2 Acas: early conciliation

  p Acas provides impartial information, advice and conciliation services on all aspects of employment law. It&#39;s available to employers and to employees.

  p Before making a claim to an employment tribunal you must contact Acas (Advisory, Conciliation and Arbitration Service) to use their free Early Conciliation service. This service aims to sort out problems without having to go to an employment tribunal.

  p To use this service, fill in the Acas early conciliation notification form (which can be found on the Acas website), or contact Acas:

  p
    ' Phone: 0300 123 1100
